title: Bio-Techne Breaks Below 200-Day Moving Average - Notable for TECH - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Tuesday, shares of Bio-Techne Corp (Symbol: TECH) crossed below their 200 day moving average of $187.60, changing hands as low as $187.15 per share. Bio-Techne Corp shares are currently trading off about 2.3% on the day.
